# shields.io
Link generator shields.io for Modrinth

You can use this page to generate icons for your github repository to show everyone how many downloads your project has on Modrinth.

**Now you can use this: https://modrinth-utils.vercel.app/**

## Examples

### Downloads

> Project ID: [AANobbMI](https://modrinth.com/mod/sodium)
>
> Type: downloads
>

### Custom types
You can use any other options. Use the [Modrinth API documentation](https://github.com/modrinth/labrinth/wiki/API-Documentation#Mod) for other types.

![updated](https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?color=5da545&label=modrinth&prefix=updated%20&query=updated&url=https://api.modrinth.com/api/v1/mod/AANobbMI&style=flat-square&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)
